And just searching on the Internet to help
my business, I came across the RISE contest

5
00:00:14.020 --> 00:00:17.020
run by the New York City Economic
Development Corporation.

6
00:00:17.028 --> 00:00:21.007
And the purpose was to find
new technologies that would make

7
00:00:21.011 --> 00:00:25.002
