Superstorm Sandy more resilient.

8
00:00:26.008 --> 00:00:28.013
Solatube is a daylighting device.

9
00:00:29.001 --> 00:00:30.003
It's installed on the roof.

10
00:00:30.017 --> 00:00:31.019
The dome captures the light.

11
00:00:32.012 --> 00:00:35.008
The light is transferred down
through a highly reflective tube.

12
00:00:35:10 --> 00:00:38:03
And a diffuser spreads the
light out evenly in the room.

13
00:00:39.004 --> 00:00:42.003
My proposal was that I could
take 40 local businesses,

14
00:00:42.017 --> 00:00:43.015
daylight them,

15
00:00:43.019 --> 00:00:45.011
thereby saving them electricity,

16
00:00:45.017 --> 00:00:47.009
less strain on the power grid,

17
00:00:47.010 --> 00:00:51.000
and providing a safety factor for them
in case of future blackouts.

18
00:00:53.008 --> 00:00:56.003
