in a lot of other areas in the city,

23
00:01:05.017 --> 00:01:07.009
they're old and they're overtaxed.

24
00:01:07.029 --> 00:01:09.011
So if we do have a blackout,

25
00:01:09.013 --> 00:01:12.001
the businesses can operate
and not worry about the lighting.

26
